Runtime Dependencies

For Full Functionality:

Ollama server must be running: ollama serve
Write permissions to /tmp/ directory
Network access for HTTP servers on specified ports

Optional Dependencies
For Production Deployment:

gunicorn - WSGI server for production Flask deployment
supervisor - Process management
nginx - Reverse proxy (if needed)

For Development:

pytest - Testing framework
black - Code formatting
flake8 - Code linting

Platform Compatibility

Linux - Fully supported
macOS - Fully supported
Windows - Supported (may need to adjust file paths from /tmp/ to appropriate Windows temp directory)
